    "answer_id" : 22782035,
    "question_id" : 16891182,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I solved it by using the default password for cacerts keystore : <code>'changeit'</code></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1821511,
      "reputation" : 7522,
      "user_id" : 1655478,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 33,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/5424ecc7236cd16441fafd0d584eb7c5?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "dessalines",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1655478/dessalines"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 19,
    "last_activity_date" : 1428709020,
    "creation_date" : 1428709020,
    "answer_id" : 29572245,
    "question_id" : 16891182,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Using changeit for the password is important too. </p>\n\n<p>This command finally worked for me(with jetty):</p>\n\n<pre><code> keytool -genkey -keyalg RSA -alias selfsigned -keystore keystore.jks -storepass changeit -validity 360 -keysize 2048\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1481635,
      "reputation" : 4471,
      "user_id" : 1390874,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 67,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/7YKKV.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "goRGon",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1390874/gorgon"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 4,
    "last_activity_date" : 1443056058,
    "creation_date" : 1443056058,
    "answer_id" : 32751728,
    "question_id" : 16891182,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Summarizing the advices from this page, I finished up with the following:</p>\n\n<pre><code>keytool -genkeypair -keystore ~/.android/release.keystore -alias &lt;my_alias&gt; -storepass &lt;my_cert_pass&gt; -keyalg RSA\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then I got a set of questions regarding name, organization, location and password for my alias.</p>\n"
  }, {
