    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>keytool error: java.io.IOException: Keystore was tampered with, or password was incorrect</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>I solved my problem when I changed keystore path <strong>C:\\MyWorks\\mykeystore</strong> to <strong>C:\\MyWorks\\mykeystore.keystore</strong>.</p>\n"
