    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Check your home folder <code>~/.gradle/gradle.properties</code>. Sometimes if you have <code>gradle.properties</code> in home directory it takes details from the there. Either you can change that or delete the files. Then it will take required details from your local folder.</p>\n"
