    "body" : "<p>If you already have a <code>.store</code> file, you have to use the same password as you did to generate it. So in my case the solution was:</p>\n<pre><code>rm *.store\nrm *.cer\n</code></pre>\n<p>That may sound odd to you but I'm just trying to learn about <code>keytool</code> and am source controlling my tutorial files and rerunning them later!</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 14487083,
      "reputation" : 149,
      "user_id" : 10464617,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/7e03f9a4f38701df4ab771abd240877b?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Salah",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/10464617/salah"
    },
